paper_abstract: For some extremal (optimal) odd unimodular lattice L in dimensions 12, 16, 20, 28, 32, 36, 40, and 44, we determine all integers k such that L contains a k-frame. This result yields the existence of an extremal Type I Z(k)-code of lengths 12, 16, 20, 32, 36, 40, and 44, and a near-extremal Type I Z(k)-code of length 28 for positive integers k with only a few exceptions.
paper_title: Extremal Type I Z(k)-Codes and k-Frames of Odd Unimodular Lattices
